}}'''老人斑'''是出現在皮肤上的斑点，老人斑的出現与[[衰老|衰老]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Age spots (liver spots) - Diagnosis and treatment - Mayo Clinic|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/age-spots/diagnosis-treatment/drc-20355864|accessdate=2020-07-07|work=www.mayoclinic.org|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214005508/https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/age-spots/diagnosis-treatment/drc-20355864|dead-url=no}}</ref>和暴露在太阳下的[[紫外线|紫外线]]辐射有关<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ultraviolet (UV) Radiation|url=https://www.cancer.org/cancer/cancer-causes/radiation-exposure/uv-radiation.html|accessdate=2020-07-07|work=www.cancer.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430142949/https://www.cancer.org/cancer/cancer-causes/radiation-exposure/uv-radiation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。老人斑的颜色从浅褐色<ref>{{Cite web|title=5 skin spots you shouldn't worry about|url=https://www.health.harvard.edu/skin-and-hair/5-skin-spots-you-shouldnt-worry-about|accessdate=2020-07-07|author=Publishing|first=Harvard Health|work=Harvard Health|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227134333/https://www.health.harvard.edu/skin-and-hair/5-skin-spots-you-shouldnt-worry-about|dead-url=no}}</ref>到红色或黑色不等，且出現在人體最经常暴露在阳光下的部位，特别是手、脸、肩膀、手臂和前额上，如果一個人是秃头，其头皮上亦有可能出現老人斑。

老人斑一度被错误地认为是由[[肝脏|肝脏]]问题引起的，但老人斑与肝脏问题無關<ref>Karen J. Carlson, Stephanie A. Eisenstat, Terra Diane Ziporyn, ''The new Harvard guide to women's health'', Harvard University Press, 2004, p. 337.</ref>。一個人从40岁起，其暴露在阳光下的皮肤的再生能力開始下降，这个年龄段的人出現老人斑的情況其實非常常见<ref>{{Cite web|title=Age spots: Causes, symptoms, and treatment|url=https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/323287|accessdate=2020-07-07|date=2018-10-09|work=www.medicalnewstoday.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123212648/https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/323287|dead-url=no}}</ref>，尤其是經常在阳光下呆的人更容易出現老人斑。

在绝大多数情况下，老人斑不会对人体造成威胁，出現老人斑的人也不需要治疗，但老人斑偶尔也会影响到對[[皮肤癌|皮肤癌]]的檢測和發現。尽管老人斑是一种良性疾病，但有些人认为老人斑非常难看，並想方設法将其去除。这可以通过[[电外科|电外科]]手术、激光治疗、[[冷療|冷冻疗法]]或使用去色剂，如[[对苯二酚|对苯二酚]]<ref name="mayoclinic.org">{{Cite news|url=http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/age-spots/basics/treatment/con-20030473|title=Age spots (liver spots) Treatments and drugs|work=Mayo Clinic|accessdate=2017-02-12|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213090654/http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/age-spots/basics/treatment/con-20030473|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[維A酸|維A酸]]、局部半胱胺（topical cysteamine）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Evaluation of the efficacy of cysteamine 5% cream in the treatment of epidermal melasma: a randomized double-blind placebo-controlled trial|last=Mansouri|first=P.|last2=Farshi|first2=S.|date=2015-07-01|journal=The British Journal of Dermatology|issue=1|doi=10.1111/bjd.13424|volume=173|pages=209–17|issn=1365-2133|pmid=25251767|last3=Hashemi|first3=Z.|last4=Kasraee|first4=B.}}</ref>、[[壬二酸|壬二酸]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Treatment of lentigo maligna with azelaic acid|last=Rodríguez Prieto|first=M. A.|last2=Manchado Lopez|first2=P.|date=1993-05-01|journal=International Journal of Dermatology|issue=5|doi=10.1111/j.1365-4362.1993.tb01475.x|volume=32|pages=363–64|issn=0011-9059|pmid=8505164|last3=Ruiz Gonzalez|first3=I.|last4=Suarez|first4=D.}}</ref>或[[α-羟基酸|α-羟基酸]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Overview about liver spots/age spots|url=http://www.beautynaturalskin.com/overview-about-liver-spots/|accessdate=3 July 2015|publisher=Beauty Natural Skin|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703065028/http://www.beautynaturalskin.com/overview-about-liver-spots/|dead-url=no}}</ref>来去除老年斑。

